Syntax: charge <target>

Performs a charging attack against a target, closing distance rapidly and
striking with increased force. Charge is a Warrior-line combat skill handled
by the Warrior attack system.

Charge is available to Warden-class characters and their remort descendants
(Knight, Swordsman, Crusader).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp charge bash smash headbutt
